text: African carp is a common name that may refer to several different species of fishes: * The Tana Labeo, Labeo mesops * The Cornish jack, Mormyrops anguilloides * Labeo brachypoma * Labeo coubie * Labeo cylindricus * Labeo parvus * Labeo senegalensis * Mormyrops oudoti ==See also== *Carp
title: African carp
